{"id":"5081","name":"bright-early-a-promise-is-a-promise-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: A Promise Is A Promise Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-05-27T10:15:00-05:00","tags":["AT&amp;T","bna","cheesestick theft","granny white","haircut","memorial day weekend","nashville flood","pigtails","plane crash","roadtrip","sinkhole","TDOT","willie nelson"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you are new here, you might want to <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to the RSS feed</strong></a> for updates on this topic.<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/silenus81/4641049108/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3363/4641049108_c162138656.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"162\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. With Memorial Day weekend coming up, lots of folks will be roadtripping to, from and through town.&#xA0;TDOT will be doing their part to make the weekend run smoothly by <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/tdot-announces-lane-closure-plan-memorial-day?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">suspending all construction-related lane closures, which includes I-440</a>! We can hardly believe our ears. As we mentioned yesterday, the <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=12545278\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessee Highway Patrol will be out in full force with more than 70 checkpoints set up all over the city to catch folks</a> who may have partied a little too hard before getting behind the wheel.</p><ul><li><strong>Sink, baby, sink. </strong><a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12552526\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Another sinkhole opened up on Granny White Pike this morning</a>, becoming one of many that have popped up around the midstate in the wake of the flooding. Watch this terrifying video of another sinkhole <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/video/video.php?v=1179845794750&amp;ref=mf\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.facebook.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</li><li><strong>Willie&#x2019;s new &#x2018;do.</strong> Wait. <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/entertainment/23686357/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Willie Nelson chopped off his pigtails, because he was tired of maintaining them</a>? What does that even mean? In the words of the devastated fan on the internet quoted by WSMV, &#x201C;Oh Noooooo!&#x201D;</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces. </strong>Who knew that <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/21ded120-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">swiping some cheesesticks</a> was a felony? &#x2026; Another hot day with some <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/05/hot-afternoon-storms/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">pop-up storms in the afternoon</a> &#x2026; A <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12550085\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_self\">small airplane made a hard landing at BNA yesterday</a>, but fortunately no one was hurt &#x2026; An AT&amp;T employee claims she was <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12549237\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">fired for missing work because her house flooded</a>.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/silenus81/4641049108/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Silenus81</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}